=== PortalPlayer 5020 ===
[https://web.archive.org/web/20061202104042/http://www.portalplayer.com/products/documents/5020_Brief_0108_Public.pdf PP5020規格]

包含兩個[[ARM_architecture|ARM]][[處理器|處理器]]的[[系統單晶片|SoC]]，分別以75[[兆赫|兆赫]]運行。

由下列裝置使用：
*[[iPod|iPod]]：第四代、iPod Photo與第一代iPod Mini [https://web.archive.org/web/20050828045346/http://www.ipodlinux.org/PP5020][http://www.rockbox.org/twiki/bin/view/Main/PortalPlayer]{{Wayback|url=http://www.rockbox.org/twiki/bin/view/Main/PortalPlayer |date=20070108060646 }}
*[[iriver|iriver]] H10 系列 [http://www.rockbox.org/twiki/bin/view/Main/IriverH10Info#Portable_Player_5020]{{Wayback|url=http://www.rockbox.org/twiki/bin/view/Main/IriverH10Info#Portable_Player_5020 |date=20070226221103 }}[http://www.rockbox.org/twiki/bin/view/Main/PortalPlayer]{{Wayback|url=http://www.rockbox.org/twiki/bin/view/Main/PortalPlayer |date=20070108060646 }}
* Philips HDD100/120（未經證實，檔案格式及規格與下方的YH-925相符）
* ROCdigital rocbox model 14003
* Samsung YH-925 [https://web.archive.org/web/20060529233300/http://www.samsungplay.com/en/925.htm] 中指出"Platform: PP5020"
* Samsung YEPP YH-820MC（根據 [https://web.archive.org/web/20070103095617/http://www.tgdaily.com/2005/11/29/teardown_iriver_h10/]）
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070114074056/http://en.europe.eliohome.com/product_m310_01.html Tatung Elio M310]（system/pp5020.mi4 包含"PP5020AF-05.11-TG01-11.40-TG01-11.40-DT"一行與"Copyright(c) 1999 - 2003 PortalPlayer, Inc."）
* Virgin player 5GB（根據 [https://web.archive.org/web/20060113021847/http://www.virginelectronics.com/faq-player_5gb.htm]）
* [http://www.msi.com.tw/program/support/download/dld/spt_dld_detail.php?UID=622&kind=6 MSI Megaplayer 540]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}，固件system/pp5020.mi4包含"PP5020AF..." 一行；在德國由ALDI以Medion MD81034的名字發售。

